comments: Barnes (TOR) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) gathers the ball on his right foot and hops consecutively on it.
Powell (DAL) and Anunoby (TOR) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Anunoby (TOR) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. DAL maintains possession.
Powell (DAL) establishes a wide screening position and illegal contact occurs with Barnes's (TOR) lower body that affects Barnes's (TOR) ability to defend.
Trent Jr. (TOR) extends an arm to Dinwiddie's (DAL) front that affects his SQBR.
Achiuwa (TOR) initiates contact with Powell's (DAL) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Bullock (DAL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Boucher (TOR).  As Powell (DAL) is in the air from contesting the shot attempt, incidental contact occurs between him and Boucher.
Boucher (TOR) makes illegal foot contact with the basketball.
Anunoby (TOR) and Powell (DAL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

Powell (DAL) makes incidental contact to Anunoby's (TOR) head/face area as they both come together during the pursuit of the rebound. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Dinwiddie (DAL) grasps Achiuwa's (TOR) jersey and immediately releases it as marginal contact occurs during the pursuit of the rebound.
As Powell (DAL) reaches in, he crowds Achiuwa's (TOR) space and initiates contact to his right arm that affects his driving shot attempt.  Achiuwa is in a normal shooting motion when contact occurs.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact with the ball last, before it goes out of bounds. DAL maintains possession.
Doncic (DAL) throws the ball off of Achiuwa's (TOR) lower body, making him last to touch the ball before it goes out of bonds. DAL maintains possession.
Anunoby (TOR) reaches in, and initiates contact to Doncic's (DAL) lower body that affects his SQBR during his drive.
Trent Jr (TOR) commits a take foul on Dinwiddie (DAL).
